---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Sikkim Travel Guide | Slow Travel with Pankhuri and Kaushal"
  description="Coming soon: Our comprehensive guide to exploring Sikkim, India."
>
  <Hero 
    title="Sikkim" 
    subtitle="A Himalayan paradise of mountains, monasteries, and culture"
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626621341517-bbf3d9990a23?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop"
  />
  
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Coming Soon</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          We're currently working on our comprehensive Sikkim travel guide based on our recent visit. 
          Check back soon for a detailed itinerary, must-see attractions, hidden gems, and practical tips for exploring this beautiful Indian state.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">What to Expect in Our Sikkim Guide</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2 text-left">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Detailed itineraries for North, East, South, and West Sikkim</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Guides to Gangtok, Pelling, Lachung, and other key destinations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Information on trekking routes, monasteries, and natural attractions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Tips for experiencing local Sikkimese cuisine and cultural practices</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Practical information on permits, transportation, and accommodations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Seasonal travel advice and best times to visit different regions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Subscribe for Updates</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Want to be notified when our Sikkim guide is published? Subscribe to our newsletter!
          </p>
          
          <form class="max-w-md mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2">
            <input 
              type="email" 
              placeholder="Your email address" 
              class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 text-gray-800 flex-grow"
              required
            />
            <button 
              type="submit" 
              class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-md font-medium transition duration-300"
            >
              Subscribe
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>